			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="696" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Raphael is encountered at the beginning of the Shar Temple. He briefs the player about the Orthon - the devil he mentions - either telling them that he personally wants it dead, or that it is between the player and their objective. He then saves them from a trap and warns them about the dangers of the temple, before vanishing.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;!!! Don't remove REALLY_ASTARION tag check from the OOM branch!!!" />
